    When I run the :new_app client command with:
      | name              | psql                                 |
      | docker_image      | <%= product_docker_repo %><image>    |
      | env               | POSTGRESQL_USER=user                 |
      | env               | POSTGRESQL_PASSWORD=redhat           |
      | env               | POSTGRESQL_DATABASE=sampledbt        |
